name: Antique Jewellery
description:
Inspired by the history of jewellery and the beauty of stained glass window ‘antique jewellery’ is adorned with beads and pearl and held together by a structured cluster of stained glass mosaic shapes, with arrangements inspired by the shape of a tiara.
The contrasting decorative elements gives the ‘antique jewellery’ a glamorous and classy look, as well as emphasis the art of mosaic and transparency of stained glass window.

name: Polka Dot Pop
description:
Polka Dot Pop lashes are designed with exceptional attention to detail and originality to reflect the modern, intellectual women with an inner playfulness.
Inspired by Pop art and the carefree spirit of the 60’s, Polka Dot Pop design puts a modern twist on pop style by balancing a sophisticated look with elaborate and elegant adornments to the design.

name: Rose- British Collection’
description: PAPERSELF brings to you ‘British Collection’ a celebration of Britain’s craftsmanship, inventiveness and sprit.This collection celebrates Queens Diamond Jubilee in U.K. and London taking the central stage for Olympic and Paralympic games.

name: Lace Garden
description:
Paper false eyelashes inspired by nineteenth century French silk bobbin lace, held in the collection at the Victoria and Albert Museum, London.
Lashes launched 2011 September with V&A Museum, London.
